{"tid":1137554,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"香港出唔出到一個Billie Eilish?","createTime":"2019-05-04T01:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T05:10:46.000Z","uid":135867,"like":33,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"8f03ffd56ce80476730d9860a629af3ca15cbd80","tid":1137554,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T01:17:23.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我假設入來既都知佢係邊個，唔知既我cop段wiki落來你都係唔會睇<br />\n<br />\n不過我都係照cop啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pxkbbAwER3Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpxkbbAwER3Y&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW94Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=c113f0f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pxkbbAwER3Y</a><br />\n<br />\n2016年，比莉因她的首支單曲《Ocean Eyes（英語：Ocean Eyes (song)）》走紅，她的第一張迷你專輯《Don't Smile at Me》釋出於隔年8月隨著這張迷你專輯的大獲成功，Apple Music於2017年9月將比莉提名為其最新的「Up Next」藝人[4]。 她的首張錄音室專輯《當我們睡了 怪事發生了》釋出於2019年3月29日[5]。<br />\n在她的首張專輯發行後，比莉於美國銷量達到3百萬份，且全球總銷量約為730萬份。與此同時她的音樂於Spotify和YouTube已累積了約39億的觀看流量[6]。在美國唱片業協會認證下，比莉已累積了七支金單曲和兩支白金單曲[7]。"},{"pid":"8612b15ec7d0936971b4d5bb52042f77e3ff7308","tid":1137554,"uid":247839,"like":82,"dislike":13,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T01:20:55.000Z","msg":"感覺上麥浚龍係做緊啲咁上下嘅野<br />\n但就無乜人關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c4d1b9b7e2cdae52c06c55c826cd3f2c812164","tid":1137554,"uid":82224,"like":21,"dislike":25,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T01:29:57.000Z","msg":"聽過 唔識欣賞"},{"pid":"4717c47ba094c615632661aeb208ac054a6e536f","tid":1137554,"uid":43804,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:09:19.000Z","msg":"首先人地爸媽係演員，哥哥係歌手，又肯栽培個妹<br />\n香港個個都係考試考試考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋啲歌路咁另類，實一大班道德撚追擊啦"},{"pid":"9babdf41e4ef7c330cf55007fb82f995af91c186","tid":1137554,"uid":555,"like":4,"di